<ul>
  <li>App/Interface - which includes interface kits, applications and support;</li>
  <li>BFS - Be File System), almost complete task, with the OpenBFS system used not only by Haiku but also by SkyOS;</li>
  <li>Game - which develops the kit for games and their APIs;</li>
  <li>Input Server - the server that manages input devices such as keyboards, mice and how they communicate with other parts of the system;</li>
  <li>Kernel - the core of the operating system;</li>
  <li>Media - developing the audio server and related APIs;</li>
  <li>Network, OpenGL, Translation and other teams.</li>
</ul>

