<p>Some kits were considered complete and the others are in different stages of development.</p>

<ul>
  <li>The official website is: <a href="https://www.haiku-os.org/">https://www.haiku-os.org/</a></li>
  <li>The download can be done at: <a href="https://www.haiku-os.org/get-haiku/">https://www.haiku-os.org/get-haiku/</a> and is currently in version R1 Beta 2</li>
</ul>

